metadata.name: HOME #1
metadata.description: welcome HOME. otherhomes are a collection of 1,111 randomly generated living-spaces. owning a HOME not only means owning a safe space in the web3 realm but also contributes to giving unhoused people a safe space IRL. 50% of all primary sales go towards housing the unhoused. we want to invite people into our HOMEs, connect and make all feel welcome, just like we would in the real world. otherhomes are composed of carefully curated traits, giving their owners highly individualized artworks that feel light and inviting. A room with a view, a place to lay your hat, a path to extending the beauty of web3 out to the physical world.
